    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six features a fully overhauled VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to an 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for exceptional traction. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications, and the cooling system has been refreshed with an aluminum radiator. Finished in a flawless factory coat with an immaculate interior, this chassis retains its original suspension geometry and bushings, providing the tactile feedback and mechanical purity that defined an era. Maintenance is documented with a comprehensive service binder.",
